parameters:
It doesn't seem like it will open with the usual
methods.

Finally, you've arrived... I can't afford to lose
again and again. I'll open up, Konoha!

......So it's you, Konoha...... It's pathetic... I
was defeated by a vile demon......

It's reckless to go alone, especially in a
dangerous dungeon like this.

I'm sorry... Even though I repaid your kindness
with betrayal, you're still helping me... You're a
strange magical girl.

What are you saying? We can't just let it end like
this. You have to become my ally properly!

Kakka!!! Interesting!!! It's been a while since
I've seen a gutsy magical girl like you.

Hmmm, if it's you, we might be able to defeat that
demon...

Very well, Konoha. I shall become your servant.
After all, you have saved me twice. I cannot be
ungrateful any longer.

I hate to ask for a favor in return, but would you
let me join you in subjugating the demon that
lurks deep within here?

I must surely take down {them} with my own
hands... {They} are my archenemy.

Alright, I understand. But let's make sure to
prepare properly first. From now on, let's
continue to work together, Tenko. From now on,
let's continue to work together, Tenko.
A new loli monster has joined the party!
ShowInfo テンコが仲間になった！
